query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('axiom-of-choice',
'distribution-theory',
'epsilon-delta',
'fourier-series',
'graphing-functions',
'inner-product-space',
'inverse',
'irreducible-polynomials',
'laplace-transform',
'lie-algebras',
'numerical-linear-algebra',
'residue-calculus',
'transformation');
